{"data":[{"date":"20:11 19/07","title":"M\u1ea5t Alisson, s\u1ebfp Roma v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/mat-alisson-sep-roma-van-day-tu-tin.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Monchi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 AS Roma. Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y tham v\u1ecdng d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t, m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Alisson sang Liverpool.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Alisson chuy\u1ec3n sang Liverpool</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i, Liverpool chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson Becker. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn y\u00eau c\u1ea7u 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a AS Roma v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3n tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Brazil \u0111\u1ebfn ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlisson \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f9ng Roma. T\u1ea1i Serie A, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 28 b\u00e0n sau 38 v\u00f2ng, g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng gi\u00fap Giallorossi c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u1ea1i Champions League, anh c\u00f9ng Roma l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua s\u00e1t n\u00fat Liverpool 6-7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Monchi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 AS Roma v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Monchi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 AS Roma v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/Monchi-phat-bieu-ve-AS-Roma-va-chuyen-nhuong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Alisson s\u1eafp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Alisson h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Liverpool tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i Roma b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u nghi ng\u1edd b\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Radja Nainggolan t\u1edbi Inter Milan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Monchi \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin v\u1ec1 Roma</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMonchi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 AS Roma trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n Alisson \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ebd t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu. \u201c\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 Alisson \u0111\u00e3 sang Liverpool\u201d, Monchi n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i xem x\u00e9t n\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u01b0u, khuy\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec3m trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1ec1 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn n\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Monchi cua Roma\" title=\"Monchi cua Roma\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Monchi-cua-Roma.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Monchi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 AS Roma v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Roma \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u00f3 Javier Pastore t\u1eeb PSG hay th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Justin Kluivert t\u1eeb Ajax. Monchi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Giallorossi v\u1eabn s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u00e1n Alisson kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thi\u1ebfu tham v\u1ecdng. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00e3 qua \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Roma c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 trong 1 n\u0103m m\u00e0 l\u00e0 trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m t\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecd bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 Kluivert hay Pastore. T\u00ecnh th\u1ebf l\u00fac n\u00e0y h\u01a1i kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, song ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Roma tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/perotti-roma-se-song-tot-khi-alisson-ra-di-176-191568.html\">Perotti: Roma s\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t d\u00f9 m\u1ea5t Alisson v\u00e0o tay Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-alisson-xac-nhan-roi-roma-toi-liverpool-voi-gia-sieu-khung-172-191549.html\">N\u00f3ng: Alisson x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eddi Roma t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/kevin-strootman-khong-ngai-doi-dau-ronaldo-tai-serie-a-176-191088.html\">Sao Roma kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ronaldo c\u1ee7a Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/chinh-thuc-xac-dinh-ben-do-moi-cua-nainggolan-176-189657.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Nainggolan</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4394","checkdouble":"191624"},{"date":"19:35 19/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 19/7: Ph\u1edbt l\u1edd M.U, sao Bayern t\u00ednh t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-197-phot-lo-mu-sao-bayern-tinh-tai-ngo-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 19/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Ajax c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Barca v\u00e0 Man City.</strong> Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Marc Overmars c\u1ee7a Ajax m\u1edbi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Barca v\u00e0 Man City kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed th\u1eddi gian theo \u0111u\u1ed5i nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd nh\u01b0 Frenkie de Jong hay Matthijs de Ligt. Theo \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00ean ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i khi Ajax mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ph\u1edbt l\u1edd M.U, sao Bayern t\u00ednh t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Barca. </strong>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7  Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Barcelona h\u01a1n l\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p  \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man United. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Allianz  Arena m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i CLB c\u0169.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 197 Sao Bayern t\u00ednh t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 197 Sao Bayern t\u00ednh t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/thiago-alcantara.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Thiago mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca thay v\u00ec M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Courtois, Real ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd.</strong> Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Thibaut Courtois t\u1eeb Chelsea sang Real Madrid s\u1ebd t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn g\u00ec. L\u00fd do l\u00e0 b\u1edfi ph\u00eda Chelsea mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho \u0111\u1ea1i gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nSturridge n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf Liverpool? </strong>Daniel Sturridge ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Liverpool. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Anfield \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Deschamps quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0\u1eddng gh\u1ebf HLV Ph\u00e1p cho Zidane.</strong> HLV Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p sau World Cup 2018. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Deschamps phat bieu ve DT Phap sau World Cup 2018\" title=\"HLV Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p sau World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/hlv-deschamps-phat-bieu-ve-dt-phap-sau-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Deschamps ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0110T\u00a0Ph\u00e1p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Wilshere so s\u00e1nh HLV West Ham v\u1edbi Wenger. </strong>Wilshere so s\u00e1nh Pellegrini v\u1edbi Wenger. Anh r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i West Ham \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng khi kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Philippines d\u1ef1 AFF Cup. </strong>C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f3 tin n\u00e0y \u0111ang x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao mang qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch Ph\u00e1p nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1ed1c Philippines, Alphonse Areola. Anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 23 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Les Bleus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng cao c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4393","checkdouble":"191623"},{"date":"20:38 19/07","title":"Nh\u0103m nhe sao tr\u1ebb, Barca nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o g\u1eaft t\u1eeb Ajax","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/ajax-gui-canh-bao-danh-thep-toi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barcelona \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Frenkie de Jong v\u00e0 Matthijs de Ligt c\u1ee7a Ajax. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao, Marc Overmars ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ajax l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ea7y c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca nh\u1eafm c\u00e1c sao tr\u1ebb Ajax</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o Ajax c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan lu\u00f4n thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o h\u00e0ng uy t\u00edn nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. H\u00e0ng n\u0103m, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y cho ra m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng song \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Frenkie de Jong v\u00e0 Matthijs de Ligt \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm. Trong \u0111\u00f3, Barcelona \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1t s\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t khi d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3 c\u1eb7p t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Ajax.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Overmars ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ajax \u0111\u1ea7y c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Overmars ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ajax \u0111\u1ea7y c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/tien-ve-Frenkie-de-Jong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">De Jong n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDe Jong (21 tu\u1ed5i) l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Barca. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, De Ligt m\u1edbi 18 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Ajax v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 7 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T H\u00e0 Lan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ajax t\u1ecf ra c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao, Marc Overmars ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ajax. \u00d4ng nh\u1eafn Barca r\u1eb1ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau binh. \u201cDe Jong kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e1n, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c b\u00ean li\u00ean quan\u201d, Overmars n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u1edd De Telegraaf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u0103m nhe sao tr\u1ebb, Barca nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o g\u1eaft t\u1eeb Ajax h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u0103m nhe sao tr\u1ebb, Barca nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o g\u1eaft t\u1eeb Ajax h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Nham-nhe-sao-tre,-Barca-nhan-canh-bao-gat-tu-Ajax-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Overmars ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ajax kh\u00e1 c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0 De Ligt. C\u00e1c CLB quan t\u00e2m s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef1 do tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00e0o n\u0103m t\u1edbi. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Davinson Sanchez (t\u1edbi Tottenham) n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i cho th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 19, 20 tu\u1ed5i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi t\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-barca-cap-ben-nou-camp-nho-neymar-180-191543.html\">T\u00e2n binh Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Nou Camp nh\u1edd Neymar</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-quyet-dau-voi-real-vi-eden-hazard-180-191467.html\">Barca quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Real v\u00ec Eden Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/andre-gomes-muon-toi-tottenham-172-191411.html\">Sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Barca mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f9ng Harry Kane t\u1ea1i Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-vuot-mat-arsenal-vu-tien-ve-nzonzi-180-191340.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Arsenal v\u1ee5 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chan-mu-pogba-co-dong-thai-san-sang-dau-quan-cho-barca-172-191187.html\">Ch\u00e1n M.U, Pogba c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4392","checkdouble":"191626"},{"date":"22:29 19/07","title":"M.U \u0111\u00f3n tin c\u1ef1c vui v\u1ec1 Alexis Sanchez","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/22/mu-don-tin-cuc-vui-ve-alexis-sanchez.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Alexis Sanchez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i M.U. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 khi nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 visa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft xong visa</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i 15/7 v\u1eeba qua, Man United \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00ean m\u00e1y bay sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ri\u00eang ng\u00f4i sao Alexis Sanchez c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadp c\u1ea3nh v\u00e0o x\u1ee9 c\u1edd hoa. L\u00fd do l\u00e0 b\u1edfi anh \u0111ang th\u1ee5 \u00e1n t\u00f9 treo 16 th\u00e1ng v\u00ec b\u1ecb k\u1ebft t\u1ed9i tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 sang M\u1ef9, Sanchez bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i quay l\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m Carrington t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh. Trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3, CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n M.U \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u1eefng kh\u00fac m\u1eafc cho tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Chile.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sanchez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sanchez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/Sanchez-duoc-phep-sang-My-du-dau-cung-toan-doi-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sanchez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadt may l\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n sau c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft. Sanchez ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng minh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00fang ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt trong th\u1eddi gian h\u01b0\u1edfng \u00e1n treo v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U b\u1ea3o l\u00e3nh. Anh m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p visa sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Club America (Mexico) v\u00e0o 9h s\u00e1ng mai (20/7).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho th\u1edf ph\u00e0o</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin Sanchez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u khi\u1ebfn HLV Jose Mourinho c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vui m\u1eebng. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y m\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean x\u1ee9 c\u1edd hoa. Nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u1edf \u0111i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ph\u00e9p th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho va Sanchez\" title=\"Mourinho va Sanchez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/22/Sanchez-chia-se-ve-khoi-dau-kho-khan-o-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mourinho nh\u1eadn tin vui t\u1eeb Sanchez</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRi\u00eang c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh, Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh M.U s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a. T\u00ednh ra, s\u1ebd c\u00f3 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Premier League do ch\u01b0a k\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u0129. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec th\u1ebf, vi\u1ec7c Sanchez c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf M\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft h\u01a1n. Mourinho mu\u1ed1n ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile t\u1eadp d\u01b0\u1ee3t c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League v\u1edbi Leicester v\u00e0o r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 11/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Man United tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lich-thi-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-cua-mu-172-191607.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/adnan-januzaj-sap-tro-lai-ngoai-hang-anh-doi-dau-mu-172-191599.html\">Adnan Januzaj s\u1eafp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhan-don-dau-vu-bonucci-172-191595.html\">MU nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Italia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-co-vai-loi-muon-gui-den-paul-pogba-172-191552.html\">Mourinho c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Paul Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-danh-ca-cum-bayern-munich-172-191550.html\">MU mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh c\u1ea3 c\u1ee5m Bayern Munich</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4391","checkdouble":"191630"},{"date":"05:45 20/07","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Liverpool k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Alisson","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.</h2><h2><br>\r\nLiverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Alisson<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Alisson Becker t\u1eeb AS Roma, theo m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn <strong>65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng &ndash; bao g\u1ed3m ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 56 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, c\u00f9ng 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed,</strong> v\u01b0\u1ee3t xa k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u0169 34,7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Ederson.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Liverpool, sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i Melwood ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Alisson Becker \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Loris Karius &ndash; th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda trong khung g\u1ed7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" title=\"Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h2>Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3m ngh\u0129 khi \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a CLB, m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u00ecnh Liverpool. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i&rdquo; &ndash; Alisson Becker h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 \u0110T Brazil \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 17/37 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Serie A, v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 cao th\u1ee9 3 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u &ndash; ch\u1ec9 sau Jan Oblak v\u00e0 David De Gea. Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool, khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 Fabinho, Keita v\u00e0 Shaqiri m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-blackburn-02-liverpool-giao-huu-he-2018-326-191631.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/tong-hop-blackburn-02-liverpool-giao-huu-he-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-blackburn-02-liverpool-giao-huu-he-2018-326-191631.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Blackburn 0-2 Liverpool (Giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018)</span><br>\r\nHai pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng trong hi\u1ec7p 2 c\u1ee7a Markovic v\u00e0 Sturridge gi\u00fap L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Premier League nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t trong...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mat-alisson-sep-roma-van-day-tu-tin-176-191624.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/mat-alisson-sep-roma-van-day-tu-tin.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mat-alisson-sep-roma-van-day-tu-tin-176-191624.html\">M\u1ea5t Alisson, s\u1ebfp Roma v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin</span><br>\r\nMonchi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 AS Roma. Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y tham v\u1ecdng d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t, m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Alisson sang...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4390","checkdouble":"191632"},{"date":"06:20 20/07","title":"Alisson n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/alisson-noi-gi-khi-chinh-thuc-gia-nhap-liverpool.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Anfield. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool, sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nAlisson ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 chi ti\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed trong tr\u1eadn Liverpool 5-2 AS Roma &ndash; b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. S\u1ef1 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a C\u0110V L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf t\u1ea1i Anfield l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn anh \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, bom t\u1ea5n 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool cho bi\u1ebft: <em>&ldquo;Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. Khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0u \u00e1o, thay \u0111\u1ed5i CLB, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n thay \u0111\u1ed5i to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, gia \u0111\u00ecnh, v\u1ee3 v\u00e0 con g\u00e1i t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</em></div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Liverpool vs Roma r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u0169ng theo d\u00f5i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i vui m\u1eebng khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;Liverpool l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3, n\u01a1i c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Hy v\u1ecdng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p v\u00e0o qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a CLB.</em><strong><em> Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y Liverpool l\u1edbn m\u1ea1nh m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.&rdquo;</em></strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/ali.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Salah</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alisson s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 2 sau 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Roma, sau ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mohamed Salah. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp, Alisson cho bi\u1ebft: <em>&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean l\u1ea1c v\u1edbi nhau nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi anh \u1ea5y r\u1eddi Roma. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i khi 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 4.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;H\u00f4m qua, anh \u1ea5y g\u1eedi cho t\u00f4i m\u1ed9t tin nh\u1eafn: &lsquo;N\u00e0y, c\u1eadu c\u00f2n ch\u1edd g\u00ec n\u1eefa&rsquo;. V\u00e0 khi cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111ang trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, t\u00f4i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi Salah: &lsquo;B\u00ecnh t\u0129nh n\u00e0o, t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e2y&rsquo;.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 vui m\u1eebng khi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Salah m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, anh \u1ea5y c\u00f2n s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u00e1 t\u00ednh l\u1edbn, nh\u00e2n c\u00e1ch tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i&rdquo;</em> &ndash; Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Liverpool k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Alisson</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/alisson-becker-ong-anh-ngo-ngao-va-vinh-quang-den-muon-389-191612.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/alisson-becker-ong-anh-ngo-ngao-va-vinh-quang-den-muon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/alisson-becker-ong-anh-ngo-ngao-va-vinh-quang-den-muon-389-191612.html\">Alisson Becker, \u00f4ng anh ng\u1ed5 ng\u00e1o v\u00e0 vinh quang \u0111\u1ebfn mu\u1ed9n</span><br>\r\nL\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a d\u1eady th\u00ec tr\u1ec5, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng trang l\u1ee9a. Trong b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra d\u1eady th\u00ec, trong khi c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee9c n\u0103m (cao...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4389","checkdouble":"191633"},{"date":"06:36 20/07","title":"Klopp chia s\u1ebb nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. HLV Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Alisson v\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Klopp ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">56 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn Alisson Becker tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi &ndash; v\u01b0\u1ee3t xa nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 m\u1ec7nh gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o (Ederson v\u00e0 Buffon). Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi Liverpool, ti\u1ec1n nong kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, b\u1edfi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Alisson, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho bi\u1ebft:<em> &ldquo;Trong v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n qua, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t &ndash; v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 nhi\u1ec1u. Th\u00fa th\u1ef1c, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u1ecf v\u1edbi BL\u0110. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng, v\u00ec v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m. <strong>Ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u1ec1 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3,</strong> ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, v\u00ec th\u1ebf Liverpool kh\u00f4ng suy ngh\u0129 nhi\u1ec1u. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 cho th\u1ea5y t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. S\u1ebd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u1ec7n x\u1ea3y ra trong nh\u1eefng tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Liverpool vui m\u1eebng khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu Alisson ngay b\u00e2y gi\u1edd.&rdquo;</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Alisson, bom t\u1ea5n 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Alisson, bom t\u1ea5n 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/klop.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Klopp chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfng Anh c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, v\u00e0 Alisson l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u c\u00e1 t\u00ednh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Roma v\u00e0 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao t\u1ea1i World Cup. \u0110T Brazil \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p may khi d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Alisson \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t.&rdquo;</em></div>\r\n<div><em> &nbsp;</em></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1edf h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 Alisson ph\u1ea3i th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi Premier League. Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, v\u0103n h\u00f3a, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng, b\u1edfi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson v\u00ec t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. Nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang \u0111\u1ebfn, v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi&rdquo;</em> &ndash; Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Alisson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-noi-gi-khi-chinh-thuc-gia-nhap-liverpool-172-191633.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/alisson-noi-gi-khi-chinh-thuc-gia-nhap-liverpool.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-noi-gi-khi-chinh-thuc-gia-nhap-liverpool-172-191633.html\">Alisson n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool?</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Anfield. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool, sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Liverpool k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Alisson</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/alisson-becker-ong-anh-ngo-ngao-va-vinh-quang-den-muon-389-191612.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/alisson-becker-ong-anh-ngo-ngao-va-vinh-quang-den-muon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/alisson-becker-ong-anh-ngo-ngao-va-vinh-quang-den-muon-389-191612.html\">Alisson Becker, \u00f4ng anh ng\u1ed5 ng\u00e1o v\u00e0 vinh quang \u0111\u1ebfn mu\u1ed9n</span><br>\r\nL\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a d\u1eady th\u00ec tr\u1ec5, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng trang l\u1ee9a. Trong b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra d\u1eady th\u00ec, trong khi c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee9c n\u0103m (cao...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4388","checkdouble":"191634"},{"date":"06:53 20/07","title":"V\u1edbi Alisson, Premier League chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/26/voi-alisson-premier-league-chiem-tron-hang-thu-dat-gia-nhat-hanh-tinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson Becker v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb h\u01a1n 1 t\u1ef7 b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c Liverpool c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson Becker t\u1eeb AS Roma. C\u1ed9ng c\u1ea3 ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed, t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf chi ra cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng &ndash; k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. V\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafc m\u1eafc r\u1eb1ng Ederson hay Buffon m\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t (do ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 euro).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Premier League c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 trong 2 n\u0103m (k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb 6/2016). C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Alisson, Liverpool c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Virgil Van Dijk &ndash; trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Man City d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Pep Guardiola &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Kyle Walker, John Stones v\u00e0 Benjamin Mendy.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Premier League chi\u1ebfm n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Premier League chi\u1ebfm n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/Premier-League-chiem-nua-doi-hinh-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alisson gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nTr\u00ean h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u0169ng g\u00f3p 1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u00e0 Paul Pogba &ndash; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2016 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. X\u00e9t theo v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3, 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Pogba trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 James Rodriguez (71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) v\u00e0 Philippe Coutinho (142 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng).</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo l\u0129nh x\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 115 tri\u1ec7u euro (99,2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) khi gia nh\u1eadp Juventus m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ee7a PSG &ndash; &ldquo;k\u1ecbch s\u0129&rdquo; Neymar c\u00f9ng &ldquo;si\u00eau xe&rdquo; Kylian Mbappe.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 1056 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Premier League c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1edbi danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, khi h\u1ecd chi\u1ebfm 6/11 c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh (ch\u1ec9 x\u00e9t t\u1eebng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/team.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u1ea2nh: B/R Football</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191634.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chia-se-nguyen-nhan-bien-alisson-thanh-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191634.html\">Klopp chia s\u1ebb nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nSau nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. HLV Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Alisson v\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-noi-gi-khi-chinh-thuc-gia-nhap-liverpool-172-191633.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/alisson-noi-gi-khi-chinh-thuc-gia-nhap-liverpool.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-noi-gi-khi-chinh-thuc-gia-nhap-liverpool-172-191633.html\">Alisson n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool?</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Anfield. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi Alisson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool, sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4387","checkdouble":"191635"},{"date":"14:34 19/07","title":"Ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldo b\u1ecb in m\u1eb7t l\u00ean ... gi\u1ea5y v\u1ec7 sinh","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/ngoi-sao-ronaldo-bi-in-mat-len-giay-ve-sinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CR7 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ecbu tr\u1eadn trong cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c fan \u1edf Italy khi \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a anh xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u00f9ng trong WC.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Gi\u1ea5y v\u1ec7 sinh Ronaldo in h\u00ecnh si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0y b\u00e1n kh\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ed1 Napoli, Italy. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Higuain c\u0169ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1ch b\u00f4i nh\u1ecd n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Untitled-2-2469-1531967140.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNapoli v\u00e0 Juventus c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \"kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1eddi chung\". S\u1ef1 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y khi Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 Higuain. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u0169ng di\u1ec5n ra k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 \"B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\". Vi\u1ec7c Juventus g\u00e2y \u1ed3n \u00e0o v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng C. Ronaldo ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c khi\u1ebfn C\u0110V Napoli n\u00f3ng m\u1eaft v\u00e0 v\u1ee5 in h\u00ecnh CR7 l\u00ean gi\u1ea5y v\u1ec7 sinh nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 C. Ronaldo, c\u00e1c c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng \u1edf Napoli c\u00f2n b\u00e0y b\u00e1n nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9n gi\u1ea5y v\u1ec7 sinh c\u00f3 in h\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u CLB l\u1edbn tr\u00ean ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0 Bayern Munich, Monaco, Torino, Chelsea.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4386","checkdouble":"191598"},{"date":"16:41 19/07","title":"Alisson Becker, \u00f4ng anh ng\u1ed5 ng\u00e1o v\u00e0 vinh quang \u0111\u1ebfn mu\u1ed9n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/alisson-becker-ong-anh-ngo-ngao-va-vinh-quang-den-muon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a d\u1eady th\u00ec tr\u1ec5, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng trang l\u1ee9a. Trong b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra d\u1eady th\u00ec, trong khi c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee9c n\u0103m (cao nh\u1ea5t), t\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u1eb9t \u0111\u1eb9t t\u1ea1i m\u1ee9c hai. D\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng nghi v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 chi\u1ec1u cao, s\u1ee9c b\u1eadt, t\u00f4i \u0111i\u1ec1u thi\u1ebfu. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i b\u1ecb \u201c\u0111\u00e0y \u1ea3i\u201d tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ec3 t\u00f4i nh\u1edb xem! \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u0103m 1998, l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i tr\u00f2n n\u0103m tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng anh Muriel th\u00ec 10 tu\u1ed5i. T\u00f4i v\u00e0 \u1ed5ng c\u00f9ng xem tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 1998 gi\u1eefa Brazil v\u00e0 H\u00e0 Lan t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 d\u00ec. B\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng? B\u00e0 d\u00ec qu\u00fd h\u00f3a c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u1eb3n m\u1ed9t b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c t\u1eeb khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a di\u1ec5n ra.</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson Becker, \u00f4ng anh ng\u1ed5 ng\u00e1o v\u00e0 vinh quang \u0111\u1ebfn mu\u1ed9n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alisson Becker, \u00f4ng anh ng\u1ed5 ng\u00e1o v\u00e0 vinh quang \u0111\u1ebfn mu\u1ed9n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/al.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Alisson Becker, \u00f4ng anh ng\u1ed5 ng\u00e1o v\u00e0 vinh quang \u0111\u1ebfn mu\u1ed9n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9o \u0111\u1ebfn lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u, cha v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i y\u00ean, hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecd c\u1ee9 nh\u1ea3y nh\u00f3t tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh TV nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5t tr\u00ed. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111i\u00ean kh\u00f9ng khi Taffarel c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e1nh c\u00f4ng c\u00fa s\u00fat \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ec7nh. Cha t\u00f4i phi m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1ch t\u1eeb ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0o nh\u00e0 b\u1ebfp v\u00e0 v\u1ea5p ng\u00e3. May thay chi\u1ebfc b\u00e1nh kem tr\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ee9u cho nhan s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng m\u1ed9t pha tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cha t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng v\u1eabn mang khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7y kem ch\u1ea1y kh\u1eafp nh\u00e0, reo h\u00f2:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang ta v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft r\u1ed3i! Ch\u00fang ta v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft r\u1ed3i!&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1eaft t\u00f4i l\u00fac \u0111\u1ea5y, \u00f4ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u00e3 \u0111i\u00ean d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1ea5t tr\u1ea7n \u0111\u1eddi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n t\u00f4i sao? B\u1eadn c\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i qu\u00ean tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u lu\u00f4n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai m\u01b0\u01a1i n\u0103m sau, qu\u00fd t\u1eed c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Brazil thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch, t\u00f4i th\u1eeba h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t t\u00ed &ldquo;\u0111i\u00ean&rdquo; c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. B\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh khi ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng sao? Kh\u00f4ng, kh\u00f4ng, gi\u1ea3 v\u1edd th\u00f4i. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n b\u00e1o c\u00e1o v\u1ec1 t\u00f4i khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u00ed c\u00f3 ghi:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Alisson Becker: th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, b\u1ea3y tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00f9n. D\u1ec5 n\u1ed5i n\u00f3ng. D\u1ec5 kh\u00f3c nh\u00e8.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e2u, nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea5y. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng trong khung g\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tinh huong Alisson cuu thua xuat than\" title=\"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Alisson c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/alisson.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Alisson c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb \u00f4ng anh Muriel. Muriel h\u01a1n t\u00f4i n\u0103m tu\u1ed5i, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00ed do \u1ed5ng lu\u00f4n khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i &ldquo;n\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t&rdquo;. Muriel lu\u00f4n t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdc t\u00f4i ph\u00e1t kh\u00f3c. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u00f4ng anh trai n\u00e0o tr\u00ean \u0111\u1eddi c\u0169ng gi\u1ecfi tr\u00f2 b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t. Song nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, Muriel gi\u00fap t\u00f4i ki\u1ec1m ch\u1ebf c\u1ea3m x\u00fac, kh\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1edbn n\u00e0o th\u00edch kh\u00f3c nh\u00e8 c\u1ea3, \u0111\u00fang kh\u00f4ng?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cho \u0111\u1ebfn sau n\u00e0y t\u00f4i m\u1edbi ng\u1ed9 ra, Muriel ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn l\u1ed1i t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea3o t\u00f4i th\u1eeba h\u01b0\u1edfng gene th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n di truy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb gia \u0111\u00ecnh. M\u1eb9 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e9m th\u1eddi h\u1ecdc sinh. \u00d4ng c\u1ed1 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng b\u1eaft g\u00f4n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nghi\u1ec7p d\u01b0 t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n Novo Hamburgo. Cha t\u00f4i gi\u1eef khung th\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f4ng ty. V\u00e0 \u00f4ng anh \u0111\u00e1ng gh\u00e9t n\u1eefa. \u0110\u00e2y h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Ch\u00faa r\u1ed3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u0103m tu\u1ed5i, anh em t\u00f4i hay xem ra s\u00e2n xem cha t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f4ng ty. T\u00f4i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi phong th\u00e1i &ldquo;hoang d\u00e3&rdquo; pha ch\u00fat &ldquo;\u0111i\u00ean&rdquo; c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. Kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh, \u00f4ng lao th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eaft b\u00f3ng khi h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khung th\u00e0nh. Khi \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb xung quanh: &ldquo;Cha tao \u0111\u1ea5y! R\u1ed3i tao s\u1ebd b\u1eaft b\u00f3ng hay nh\u01b0 \u1ed5ng!&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i Muriel k\u00e9o t\u00f4i v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a \u1ed5ng. Tuy\u1ec7t! G\u00e3 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng to cao&hellip;\u0111\u1ee9a l\u00f9n nh\u1ea5t (t\u00f4i) m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eaft g\u00f4n. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;b\u00e9n duy\u00ean&rdquo; v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef khung g\u1ed7 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Klopp-phat-bieu-ve-Liverpool-va-mo-vo-doi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2002, World Cup t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Anh em t\u00f4i ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o c\u0169ng d\u1eady t\u1eeb l\u00fac b\u00ecnh minh, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb socola, b\u00e1nh ng\u00f4, s\u1eefa v\u00e0 m\u1edf TV xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. B\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5y, Brazil \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qu\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u1ea1 l\u00f9ng \u0111\u00f3, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 gi\u00e1c ng\u1ed9 trong vui s\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1eady.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u00ecnh s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c! M\u00ecnh s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Brazil! M\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn World Cup v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch!&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m \u0111\u00f3 10 tu\u1ed5i, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u trong \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i khao kh\u00e1t m\u00e3nh li\u1ec7t m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n gi\u00e0nh b\u1eaft g\u00f4n trong m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean con ph\u1ed1 Novo Hamburgo. Khi kinh t\u1ebf gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n, cha b\u00e1n c\u0103n h\u1ed9, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn c\u0103n nh\u00e0 m\u1edbi. Anh em t\u00f4i c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng gian t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng nh\u1ef1a. B\u1ecdn t\u00f4i d\u00f9ng&hellip;c\u1eeda ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch l\u00e0m khung th\u00e0nh. B\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5y, sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00faa \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Internacional t\u1ea1i Porto Alegre, m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 x\u1ecbn t\u1ea1i Brazil. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1, song, gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>T\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00f9n!</strong></em><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a d\u1eady th\u00ec tr\u1ec5, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng trang l\u1ee9a. Trong b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra d\u1eady th\u00ec, trong khi c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee9c n\u0103m (cao nh\u1ea5t), t\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u1eb9t \u0111\u1eb9t t\u1ea1i m\u1ee9c hai. D\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng nghi v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 chi\u1ec1u cao, s\u1ee9c b\u1eadt, t\u00f4i \u0111i\u1ec1u thi\u1ebfu. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i b\u1ecb &ldquo;\u0111\u00e0y \u1ea3i&rdquo; tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/nong-alisson-xac-nhan-roi-roma-toi-liverpool-voi-gia-sieu-khung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y, \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 x\u1ea3y ra khi Internacional chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh m\u1edbi t\u1eeb Palmeiras. T\u1ec7 th\u1eadt! M\u1ed9t g\u00e3 to x\u00e1c kh\u00e1c sao? T\u00f4i r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1y c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi th\u1ea5y g\u00e3.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Tuy\u1ec7t! Gi\u1edd m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 ba. Gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t r\u1ed3i&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 chi\u1ec1u cao \u00e1m \u1ea3nh t\u00f4i h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y m\u1ed7i khi b\u1eaft g\u1eb7p \u00f4ng anh cao k\u1ec1u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Muriel \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Nike Cup &ndash; gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho l\u1ee9a tu\u1ed5i 14-15. V\u00e0 \u1ed5ng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i. M\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n \u0111i ngang k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m ch\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Muriel, m\u00e1u &ldquo;\u0103n thua&rdquo; l\u1ea1i tr\u1ed7i l\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Muriel, em c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i!&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Song, t\u00f4i c\u00f2n ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u Nike Cup. T\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m, suy ngh\u0129 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn. T\u00f4i h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i t\u1eeb khung g\u1ed7: Iker Casillas v\u00e0 Gianluigi Buffon. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t khi m\u1edbi 17 tu\u1ed5i. Trong khi t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ng\u1ed3i &ldquo;m\u00f2n \u0111\u00edt&rdquo; tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 t\u1eeb b\u00e9 \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson va anh trai\" title=\"Alisson v\u00e0 anh trai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/as.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Alisson v\u00e0 anh trai</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nghi ng\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. H\u1ecd ra th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n, t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1n g\u00f3i kh\u1ecfi Internacinal.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u k\u00ec di\u1ec7u nh\u1ea5t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn. B\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng? Ch\u00faa \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf qua tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eady th\u00ec, \u00fd t\u00f4i l\u00e0 cao h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i t\u1eeb 1m70 th\u00e0nh 1m87 ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t n\u0103m. M\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 d\u1eady th\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1t ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng b\u1ed1n. Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u n\u0103m t\u00f4i 16 tu\u1ed5i, khi \u0111ang \u1edf bi\u1ec3n v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1m b\u1ea1n. Linh t\u00ednh m\u00e1ch b\u1ea3o t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng. T\u00f4i ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i: n\u0103m cu\u1ed9c g\u1ecdi nh\u1ee1 t\u1eeb \u00f4ng n\u1ed9i. Trong ph\u00fat ch\u1ed1c, nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kinh kh\u1ee7ng \u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e2m tr\u00ed t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1ecdi cho \u00f4ng, t\u00f4i nh\u01b0 ng\u1eebng th\u1edf trong kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc ch\u1edd m\u00e1y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span>\u00d4ng \u00e0? C\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec v\u1eady \u1ea1?</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span>Nh\u00f3c, ch\u00e1u ph\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 NGAY B\u00c2Y GI\u1edc!</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span>Sao \u1ea1? C\u00f3 ai b\u1ecb g\u00ec sao? C\u00f3 ai qua \u0111\u1eddi sao \u00f4ng?</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span>Kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng! Ta b\u00e1o tin ch\u00e1u v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o U17 Brazil th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed3n v\u00eda t\u00f4i quay l\u1ea1i sau ph\u00fat gi\u00e2y lo l\u1eafng c\u00f9ng c\u1ef1c. Tr\u1ea5n t\u0129nh l\u1ea1i, ch\u1ee3t nh\u1edb \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t th\u00edch \u0111\u00f9a, t\u00f4i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc xem c\u00f3 n\u00ean v\u1ec1 ngay kh\u00f4ng&hellip;cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi \u00f4ng ch\u00fa nghi\u00eam t\u00fac g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ebfn. T\u00f4i l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ch\u1ea1y m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1ch 30 ph\u00fat t\u1eeb b\u00e3i bi\u1ec3n v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edf website L\u0110B\u0110 Brazil, c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1eadp v\u00e0o m\u1eaft t\u00f4i: &ldquo;Alisson Becker&rdquo;. Ph\u1ea3i! Tuy\u1ec7t c\u00fa m\u00e8o, t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n! C\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ee3t tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Neymar v\u00e0 Coutinho, hai \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh si\u00eau sao sau n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed1n n\u0103m sau, 2013, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft Internacional khi 20 tu\u1ed5i. 2015, t\u00f4i ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n nhanh \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0o n\u00f3. Nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n, \u0111ang trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00f4i l\u1ea9m b\u1ea9m &ldquo;Wow! M\u00ecnh \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. M\u00ecnh l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Brazil. M\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i World Cup. Xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Ch\u00faa!&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Muriel.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson dang la muc tieu hang dau cua Liverpool\" title=\"Alisson \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/28/souness-phat-bieu-ve-tinh-trang-thu-mon-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Alisson v\u00e0 Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb ng\u00e0y anh em t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho c\u00f9ng c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n so s\u00e1nh &ldquo;Li\u1ec7u Alisson c\u00f3 gi\u1ecfi nh\u01b0 Muriel kh\u00f4ng?&rdquo;. Th\u1eadt l\u00f2ng, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Muriel, v\u00ec anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u1eeb b\u00e9 t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ecfi h\u01a1n Muriel, anh ta c\u0169ng th\u1ebf, \u0111\u1eddi n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n thua c\u1eadu em bao gi\u1edd. Internacional h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i khi c\u00f3 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n nh\u1edb, khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eadp th\u00eam ngo\u00e0i gi\u1edd. Muriel lu\u00f4n k\u00e8 k\u00e8 v\u00e0 qu\u00e1t v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t t\u00f4i &ldquo;C\u1ed1 l\u00ean th\u1eb1ng nh\u00f3c! T\u1eadp th\u00eam n\u00e0o!&rdquo;. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng v\u1eeba, khi th\u1ea5y \u1ed5ng m\u1ec7t, t\u00f4i tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u0169a ngay: &ldquo;Ti\u1ebfp n\u00e0o l\u00e3o gi\u00e0! Nh\u00ecn th\u1eb1ng nh\u00f3c n\u00e0y m\u00e0 l\u00e0m g\u01b0\u01a1ng!&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wow, nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y th\u01a1 b\u00e9 c\u00f9ng ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f9a v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng nh\u1ef1a. Gi\u1eefa ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ganh \u0111ua, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u1ea5t \u0111i t\u00ecnh anh em. T\u00f4i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n Muriel. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110TQG, t\u00f4i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec Brazil, t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u00ec \u00f4ng anh Muriel n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Muriel Becker sau khi r\u1eddi Internacional n\u0103m 2017 \u0111\u00e3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 Belenenses, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean th\u1ea3m c\u1ecf c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf tuy\u1ec3n, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh con ph\u1ed1 h\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i Novo Hamburgo, qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng nh\u1ef1a v\u00e0 Muriel t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n gi\u00fap t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Muriel \u00e0, n\u1ebfu anh \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng d\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, c\u1ea3m \u01a1n anh. M\u1ed7i pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a em l\u00e0 d\u00e0nh cho anh. Th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a em c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a anh. B\u1edfi v\u00ec ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 c\u00e1i k\u1ebft \u0111\u1eb9p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em><strong>L\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ecbch theo:&nbsp;https://www.theplayerstribune.com/en-us/articles/alisson-becker-this-is-for-my-brother<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n</em><strong>H\u1ea2I TH\u01af\u1ee2NG (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4385","checkdouble":"191612"},{"date":"15:18 19/07","title":"Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng: U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ng\u1ee7 qu\u00ean tr\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/8/xuan-truong-u23-viet-nam-khong-duoc-phep-ngu-quen-sau-chien-thang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ng\u1ee7 qu\u00ean tr\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i VCK ch\u00e2u \u00c1.</h2><h2>\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ng\u1ee7 qu\u00ean tr\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\"</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 v\u1eeba qua s\u1ebd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tham d\u1ef1 \u00c1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, s\u00e1ng 19/7 t\u1ea1i tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra l\u1ec5 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 Gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng bao g\u1ed3m 23 VI\u1ec7t Nam, U23 Uzbekistan, U23 Oman v\u00e0 U23 Palestine. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft gi\u00fap \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc ra s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ng\u1ee7 qu\u00ean  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ng\u1ee7 qu\u00ean  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/8/xuan-truong-u23-viet-nam-khong-duoc-phep-ngu-quen-sau-chien-thang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n HAGL cho hay: \"V\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1\u00a0gi\u00fap ch\u00fang em th\u00eam t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u\u00a0v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu m\u00e3i ng\u1ee7 qu\u00ean trong khi c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00e1c v\u1eabn ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n th\u00ec ch\u00fang\u00a0ta s\u1ebd t\u1ee5t l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1eafp t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang em l\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc trong khu v\u1ef1c r\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 may m\u1eafn. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang em l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u01a1n xa h\u01a1n\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u2018h\u00edp\u2019 cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam: \"V\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o, d\u00f9 giao h\u1eefu hay ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, c\u00e1c\u00a0c\u1ea7u\u00a0th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng cho kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3. Em s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i\u00a0b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ASIAD th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 23/7 t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. \u0110\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3/8-7/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-bo-danh-sach-dt-olympic-viet-nam-thay-park-noi-ve-co-hoi-cua-thu-mon-bui-tien-dung-168-191597.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/cong-bo-danh-sach-dt-olympic-viet-nam-thay-park-noi-ve-co-hoi-cua-thu-mon-bui-tien-dung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-bo-danh-sach-dt-olympic-viet-nam-thay-park-noi-ve-co-hoi-cua-thu-mon-bui-tien-dung-168-191597.html\">C\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, th\u1ea7y Park n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1eabn chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh n\u1ebfu th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4384","checkdouble":"191601"},{"date":"15:42 19/07","title":"S\u1ed1c: Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Philippines d\u1ef1 AFF Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/soc-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-van-co-the-khoac-ao-philippines-du-aff-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f3 tin n\u00e0y \u0111ang x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao mang qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch Ph\u00e1p, g\u1ed1c Philippines Alphonse Areola. Anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 23 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Les Bleus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng cao c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 2018 </h2><h2>Philippines ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Philippines mu\u1ed1n nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 Alphonse Areola h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Philippines mu\u1ed1n nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 Alphonse Areola h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/GettyImages-999542344.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Alphonse Areola (ph\u1ea3i) v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T Philippines</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alphonse Areola l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n sinh tr\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea1i Paris, Ph\u00e1p trong m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f3 b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Philipines. N\u0103m 2006, khi m\u1edbi 13 tu\u1ed5i anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean CLB PSG v\u00e0 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. PSG c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u1ec7 ph\u00f3ng gi\u00fap anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o \u0110T Ph\u00e1p tham d\u1ef1 VCK World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, Areola ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 3 c\u1ee7a HLV Deschamps sau Lloris v\u00e0 Steve Mandanda. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 25 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0o cho Les Bleus d\u00f9 anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1ea1i PSG.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng v\u00ec l\u00fd do ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng 1 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110TQG Ph\u00e1p n\u00ean v\u1ec1 l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, Alphonse Areola v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. N\u1eafm b\u1eaft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y, L\u0110B\u0110 Philippines \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Philippines \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Areola t\u1eeb c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 6 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Areola, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p, khi m\u00e0 Hugo Lloris v\u1eabn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, Philippines s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 tham gia AFF Cup, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:\n16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4383","checkdouble":"191606"},{"date":"16:08 19/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a CLB Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/lich-thi-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-cua-clb-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018: Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u - LT\u0110 giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Chelsea nhanh v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00e8 2018 L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00e8 2018 L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/chelsea-camisa-18-19-28-05-2018_vyoj6q4yttrd1pgckrgt0wjvj.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong h\u00e8 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 k\u00e9m th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u duy nh\u1ea5t FA Cup nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch trong Top 4 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0i ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau khi sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Maurizio Sarri v\u00e0o gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Sarri \u1edf Napoli l\u00e0 Jorginho c\u0169ng gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 51,3 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Napoli \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0m quen v\u00e0 cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u1edf London. Ng\u00e0y 23/7 t\u1edbi Chelsea s\u1ebd sang Australia \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi CLB Perth Glory. </div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong h\u00e8 2018 (gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam)</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">18h30 ng\u00e0y 23/7 Perth Glory vs Chelsea<br>\r\n01h05 ng\u00e0y 29/7 Chelsea vs Inter Milan (ICC\u00a02018)<br>\r\n02h05 ng\u00e0y 2/8 Arsenal vs Chelsea (ICC\u00a02018)<br>\r\n21h00 ng\u00e0y 5/8 Chelsea vs Manchester City (Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh - FA Community Shield)<br>\r\n02h05 ng\u00e0y 8/8 Chelsea vs Lyon (ICC\u00a02018)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4382","checkdouble":"191609"}]}